HEADWORD: Dodded
<hw>Dod"ded</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Dodd</er>.]</ety>
<def>Without horns; <as>as, <ex>dodded</ex> cattle</as>; without beards;
<as>as, <ex>dodded</ex> corn</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Halliwell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
